title: Saudis Cut Main Oil Price to 5-Year Low
description: Saudi Arabia cut the price of its flagship crude grade to the lowest level in five years.
content:
Saudi Arabia cut the price of its flagship crude grade to the lowest level in five years, amid persistent signs of a surplus in global oil markets.
